<!-- templates/budget-planner/debt-guide.hbs -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 18mm;
    }

    body {
      font-family: {{customization.fontFamily}};
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
      padding-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .intro {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .methods-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .method-card {
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 2px solid;
    }

    .method-card.snowball {
      background: #e3f2fd;
      border-color: #2196f3;
    }

    .method-card.avalanche {
      background: #fce4ec;
      border-color: #e91e63;
    }

    .method-icon {
      font-size: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .method-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .method-card.snowball .method-name { color: #1976d2; }
    .method-card.avalanche .method-name { color: #c2185b; }

    .method-how {
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .method-how-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .method-pros {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .method-pros-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      color: #388e3c;
    }

    .method-pros ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
    }

    .method-pros li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .method-best {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .method-best-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .vs-badge {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .example-section {
      background: #fff8e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .example-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f57c00;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .example-debts {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .example-debt {
      background: white;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .debt-name {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .debt-amount {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #e91e63;
    }

    .debt-rate {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #999;
    }

    .example-order {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .order-box {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .order-box.snowball { background: #e3f2fd; }
    .order-box.avalanche { background: #fce4ec; }

    .order-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .order-list {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .choice-section {
      border: 3px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .choice-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .choice-options {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .choice-option {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .choice-checkbox {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border: 2px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .quote-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{customization.primaryColor}}, {{customization.secondaryColor}});
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .quote-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .quote-meaning {
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 class="title">Mini Guide: Paying Off Debt</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Two proven strategies ‚Äî pick the one that fits your personality</p>
  </div>

  <div class="intro">
    <strong>Good news:</strong> You don't need a finance degree to get out of debt.
    You just need a plan and consistency. Here are the two most effective methods.
  </div>

  <div class="methods-grid" style="position: relative;">
    <div class="method-card snowball">
      <div class="method-icon">‚õÑ</div>
      <div class="method-name">Debt Snowball</div>
      <div class="method-how">
        <div class="method-how-title">How it works:</div>
        Pay minimum on all debts, then put extra money toward the <strong>smallest balance</strong> first.
      </div>
      <div class="method-pros">
        <div class="method-pros-title">‚úì Pros:</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Quick wins = motivation boost</li>
          <li>Fewer bills faster</li>
          <li>Psychologically satisfying</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="method-best">
        <div class="method-best-title">Best if you:</div>
        Need motivation and quick victories to stay on track
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="method-card avalanche">
      <div class="method-icon">üèîÔ∏è</div>
      <div class="method-name">Debt Avalanche</div>
      <div class="method-how">
        <div class="method-how-title">How it works:</div>
        Pay minimum on all debts, then put extra money toward the <strong>highest interest rate</strong> first.
      </div>
      <div class="method-pros">
        <div class="method-pros-title">‚úì Pros:</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Saves most money on interest</li>
          <li>Mathematically optimal</li>
          <li>Faster total payoff time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="method-best">
        <div class="method-best-title">Best if you:</div>
        Are disciplined and motivated by saving money long-term
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="example-section">
    <div class="example-title">üìù Example: You have 3 debts</div>
    <div class="example-debts">
      <div class="example-debt">
        <div class="debt-name">Credit Card A</div>
        <div class="debt-amount">$500</div>
        <div class="debt-rate">22% APR</div>
      </div>
      <div class="example-debt">
        <div class="debt-name">Credit Card B</div>
        <div class="debt-amount">$2,000</div>
        <div class="debt-rate">18% APR</div>
      </div>
      <div class="example-debt">
        <div class="debt-name">Car Loan</div>
        <div class="debt-amount">$8,000</div>
        <div class="debt-rate">6% APR</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="example-order">
      <div class="order-box snowball">
        <div class="order-title">‚õÑ Snowball order:</div>
        <ol class="order-list">
          <li>Card A ($500) ‚Üê smallest</li>
          <li>Card B ($2,000)</li>
          <li>Car Loan ($8,000)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="order-box avalanche">
        <div class="order-title">üèîÔ∏è Avalanche order:</div>
        <ol class="order-list">
          <li>Card A (22%) ‚Üê highest rate</li>
          <li>Card B (18%)</li>
          <li>Car Loan (6%)</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="choice-section">
    <div class="choice-title">‚úèÔ∏è My debt payoff strategy will be:</div>
    <div class="choice-options">
      <div class="choice-option">
        <div class="choice-checkbox"></div>
        <span>Snowball (smallest first)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="choice-option">
        <div class="choice-checkbox"></div>
        <span>Avalanche (highest interest first)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="quote-box">
    <div class="quote-text">"Every dollar you pay toward debt is buying your future freedom."</div>
    <div class="quote-meaning">The best method is the one you'll actually stick with.</div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
